data.description: Palm Beach Place presents a centrally located second-floor condo unit in West Palm Beach, featuring two bedrooms and two bathrooms. This unit offers modern comforts, including a newer kitchen with granite counters and stainless steel Whirlpool appliances, in addition to a full-size washer and dryer. The master bedroom boasts the luxury of two closets, providing ample storage space. Residents can enjoy the balcony overlooking a serene preserve. Community residents have access to a range of recreational facilities such as a fitness center, pools, tennis courts, and a designated play area for kids. With its proximity to the turnpike, commuting surrounding areas or downtown West Palm or the airport is quick and convenient.
